Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.35,0:00:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌军诺托斯舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在东北方面展开
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.41,0:00:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌军舰队开炮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.29,0:00:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二 第三装甲舰队已被锁定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.71,0:00:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌军进入我军主力舰队炮火范围
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.82,0:00:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二装甲舰队 中弹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.27,0:00:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从两翼迂回 攻击后方的软肋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.81,0:00:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照搬兵法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.01,0:00:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺托斯的司令官
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.83,0:00:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来喜欢可靠的战术
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.78,0:00:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.57,0:01:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃得不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.47,0:01:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对石头脑袋的奥兰来说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.10,0:01:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这出戏倒演得挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.18,0:01:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比预定迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.11,0:01:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真对不起你「神速」的称号 索鲁修
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.73,0:01:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令全舰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.82,0:01:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左转十六点一齐掉头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.82,0:01:47.32,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}海军用语：八点表示90度，十六点表示180度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.53,0:01:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将敌人反包围
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.44,0:01:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荣光同在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.87,0:01:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给这些归还民们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.78,0:01:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看奥古斯塔士兵的荣耀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.73,0:01:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荣光同在 奥古斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.82,0:02:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的第四舰队被称作「神速」的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.88,0:02:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让诺托斯的归还民们知道知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.34,0:02:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荣光同在 奥古斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.87,0:02:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去敌舰踪影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.68,0:02:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去敌舰踪影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.61,0:02:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续追踪也没有意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.56,0:02:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰折返
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.18,0:02:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,返回首都
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.72,0:02:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荣光同在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.39,0:02:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死神 西尔维厄斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（OP）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.55,0:04:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}Light square
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.44,0:04:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三舰队 奥兰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.28,0:04:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及第四舰队 索鲁修
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.59,0:04:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将诺托斯舰队击破
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.37,0:04:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入扫荡残敌阶段
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.66,0:04:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨德里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:04:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.58,0:05:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压制科尔博汉特之后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.75,0:05:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在追击所属不明的战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下从图兰凯旋而回 奥古斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路斯吉尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.82,0:05:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.51,0:05:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥古斯塔恩赐的舰队…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.43,0:05:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要做出这样的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.16,0:05:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很清楚 凯万已经很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.57,0:05:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 在下承受不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.29,0:05:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 凯万
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.53,0:05:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天… 平时的那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.72,0:05:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 那么请恕在下无礼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.66,0:05:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥古斯塔 请您小心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.80,0:05:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的玩耍…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.56,0:05:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦桑特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是在下不胜惶恐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道会做出让奥古斯塔摔落这等蠢事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.48,0:05:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到王都伊格拉希亚沦陷的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.20,0:05:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,图兰国内各城市也已陆续投降
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.78,0:06:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「王都陷落之时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.29,0:06:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请即刻投降 不要让战争延长」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.00,0:06:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎事前就已发出过这样的敕令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.66,0:06:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为图兰王是广为人知的稳健派
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.36,0:06:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且在目睹Exile的威力之后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.01,0:06:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到竟有如此的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.09,0:06:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exile…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闯进我们世界的不速之客
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.72,0:06:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被诅咒的归还船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.81,0:06:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了自己的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连那些归还民都已即将遗忘的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.40,0:06:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却对他们自己进行了制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.09,0:06:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有富足到能满足所有的子民
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.49,0:06:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其它Exile的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在连其所在地都还未知
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下究竟是从哪里得到了图兰钥匙的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.27,0:06:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是我们这些兵卒该考虑的问题 瓦桑特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.32,0:07:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在被叫做图兰的那片区域
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.93,0:07:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去是什么人住在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现居住在联邦东北部 哥尼亚地区的一族
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.89,0:07:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个地域的原住民
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据记录记载
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.98,0:07:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,118年前归还的图兰人从他们手中夺走了土地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.26,0:07:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥尼亚因为去年的冻灾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.32,0:07:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该过得很艰难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要快点把麦田还给他们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是奥古斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.79,0:07:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了尽快让子民们受到恩泽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.96,0:07:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾等也会倾尽全力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个议题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是关于预定在下月举行的 前任奥古斯塔的十周年追悼仪式…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 从Grand Race之后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.51,0:07:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经十年了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.89,0:08:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.09,0:08:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不去救姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.15,0:08:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我丢下就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.11,0:08:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我来 去救姐姐大人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.80,0:08:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请冷静些 米莉亚大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.61,0:08:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.51,0:08:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能理解您的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.11,0:08:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.33,0:08:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.69,0:08:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候没有别的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.87,0:08:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又知道些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.70,0:08:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须让姐姐大人活下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.59,0:08:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算为了图兰 也要让姐姐大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莉亚大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莉亚大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.48,0:08:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.27,0:08:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样子 没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.07,0:08:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她静一静吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦那群傻鸭子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.21,0:09:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在想什么呢 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.07,0:09:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然让月亮落下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是叫「Exile」的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.43,0:09:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前 载我们的先祖回来的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.27,0:09:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这玩笑开大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.69,0:09:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没有这样的大买卖了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从梅托克陷落之后吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.92,0:09:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉萨斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.43,0:09:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9万？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.74,0:09:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤成这样最多给你5万
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.14,0:09:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8万
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.06,0:09:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5万5千
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的图兰…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.69,0:09:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无比荣耀的图兰士兵们…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是图兰的主力旗舰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装着不错的组件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.71,0:09:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs35}再来…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs35}那边让开 运出来咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.68,0:09:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs35}大丰收大丰收
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}都是难得的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.03,0:09:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚进的货
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.41,0:09:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.43,0:10:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 之后也请多关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.81,0:10:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 扶摇乘风
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.02,0:10:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.79,0:10:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.14,0:10:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.41,0:10:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先在我家休息下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.23,0:10:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.07,0:10:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁涅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.34,0:10:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你说过好多次在家不可以乘Melitta的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.09,0:10:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.71,0:10:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽灵船会在坏孩子身边出现哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.32,0:10:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.29,0:10:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.53,0:11:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.81,0:11:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新伙伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.17,0:11:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伙伴?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都听说了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是苦了你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.79,0:11:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.33,0:11:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰迪都吓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.91,0:11:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.87,0:11:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房间这么乱真不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.72,0:11:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上去蒸些土豆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便歇歇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.99,0:11:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那… 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问可以稍微分点水给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.94,0:11:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.21,0:11:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是希望啊 米莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.22,0:11:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对图兰 对我来说都是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:11:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.54,0:12:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危险的 快下来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.26,0:12:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心启动了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.15,0:12:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定就会出大事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.16,0:12:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要命令我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是图兰的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主您没有接触过Vespa
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要勉强去做办不到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.51,0:12:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了的话就请放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.17,0:12:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.33,0:12:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 那是姐姐大人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.63,0:12:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那里下来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.68,0:12:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.24,0:12:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要误会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.62,0:12:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下来 坐到后面去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.49,0:13:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.06,0:13:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来做你的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪费了不少时间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然已经看不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.45,0:13:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见对方的Vanship了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎样的机体？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.13,0:13:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记号 颜色之类呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.37,0:13:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事已至此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.97,0:13:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很重要的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.69,0:13:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.30,0:13:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 什么都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连对姐姐的回忆都夺不回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.46,0:13:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的我… 什么用都没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.75,0:13:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莉亚 听着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.62,0:13:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉下右侧的控制杆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.53,0:13:58.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.15,0:14:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.78,0:14:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,图兰是用这种道具泡茶的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.73,0:14:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一直以来都是住在这里的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.06,0:14:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是几个据点中的一个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时不时会移动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.57,0:14:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们猎的鲸鱼基本都是联邦的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.84,0:14:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久了会被盯上的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.76,0:14:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.46,0:14:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时也会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.19,0:14:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过大家本来就是从联邦逃出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.81,0:14:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从联邦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.09,0:14:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦毁灭了我们的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了家园 流落到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样成为空族人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.82,0:15:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界上还有 有很多 很多很多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.37,0:15:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来到卡尔塔法尔的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.66,0:15:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是个小宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.77,0:15:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.24,0:15:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么爽快就还回来 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空族的人们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.24,0:15:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好说清楚原委 都是会理解我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回头得给她带点什么作为回报呐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.17,0:15:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用工作来抵就最好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.48,0:15:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明什么都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.20,0:15:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却只给你们添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风儿托起迷惘的双翼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.12,0:15:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空中若有烦恼之人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.79,0:15:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必要伸去助人之手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.67,0:15:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是空族的规定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是像这样被救之后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在才能在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.23,0:15:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被救之后？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.74,0:16:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是被捡来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.25,0:16:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是落到这边了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.67,0:16:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.51,0:16:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.45,0:16:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿塔莫拉 快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.72,0:16:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.16,0:16:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个在哭的婴儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.49,0:16:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.40,0:16:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总是只想着自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为痛苦悲伤的只有我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.77,0:16:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 其实大家都一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也有你的痛苦 你的悲伤…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.68,0:17:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不能说完全不会寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.12,0:17:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那时候还太小 什么都没记住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.35,0:17:13.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以没什么感觉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.91,0:17:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我还有吉泽和吉泽的家人们在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空族的各位也都像我的家人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.25,0:17:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且只要我还在这天上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.90,0:17:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总会在某时某地 遇到认识我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.68,0:17:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我有一个梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.21,0:17:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Race？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.64,0:17:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时的你才刚刚出生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.59,0:17:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和法姆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.43,0:17:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和爸爸一起去看了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.59,0:17:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚集全世界的Vanship赛手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.23,0:17:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行一场无与伦比的竞赛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.69,0:17:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦与所有的国家缔结和平契约
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.99,0:17:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为那一日纪念
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.25,0:18:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Race的复活？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.08,0:18:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够再一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像那一天一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.36,0:18:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚集世界各地的Vanship赛手 进行竞赛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是空族 还是地上各国的赛手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.91,0:18:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 在同一片天空飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很美妙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 优胜的一定是我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.59,0:18:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 非常美妙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.40,0:18:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 好像在那场竞赛之后…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.21,0:18:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果和平还是被打破了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.72,0:18:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竞赛再也没有兴起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.39,0:18:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界各地的Vanship赛手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.59,0:18:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也散落在各自的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.80,0:18:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优胜奖杯在这里 也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.96,0:18:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Race的胜出者是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.06,0:18:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.55,0:18:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.73,0:18:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.18,0:18:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界各地的人们聚集在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.82,0:19:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仰望没有纷争的和平天空 一起欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.32,0:19:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能成真的话 那该有多么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.91,0:19:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会成真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.39,0:19:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.36,0:19:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.21,0:19:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送魂火
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.37,0:19:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 图兰的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.34,0:19:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逝去的翅膀归还天空
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是 空族的规定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.89,0:20:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿那些逝去的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.38,0:20:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平安返回天空的彼端
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.36,0:20:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O RA KA E
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.30,0:20:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TO DE TA I
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.45,0:20:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与这艘船儿来天上生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.17,0:20:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天空生活是我们的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.78,0:20:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.10,0:20:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.50,0:20:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿那些飞向天空的翅膀 一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.39,0:21:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O RA KA E
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TO DE TA I
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.38,0:21:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O RA KA E
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.79,0:21:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TO DE TA I
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.43,0:21:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.84,0:21:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必客气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.26,0:21:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和往常一样 很好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.75,0:21:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.24,0:21:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.33,0:22:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆 听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.85,0:22:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听到一条很好玩的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.62,0:22:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好玩的东西 从你嘴里说出来就肯定不是什么好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.89,0:22:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在米兰的望鲸哨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.68,0:22:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目击到了那艘死神西尔维厄斯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.31,0:22:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉泽 米莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.10,0:22:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.26,0:22:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 这么突然
